@startuml
title 生命周期工作流 - 数据血缘图
skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "entry.setting /\nstrategy_full_config /\nconfig/*.toml" as ConfigInput
rectangle "service_activation /\nstrategy_contracts /\nsubscription_config" as NormalizedConfig
rectangle "领域服务 / 聚合根 /\nGateway / Persistence" as RuntimeParts
rectangle "历史快照 / OMS 数据 /\n历史 bars" as RecoveryInputs
rectangle "已装配的 StrategyEntry" as ReadyEntry

ConfigInput --> NormalizedConfig : 读取 / 归一化
NormalizedConfig --> RuntimeParts : 构建依赖
RecoveryInputs --> RuntimeParts : 恢复 / 预热
RuntimeParts --> ReadyEntry : 注入宿主对象
@enduml
